{"id":"5549","name":"bright-early-merrily-we-roll-along","title":"Bright &amp; Early: Merrily We Roll Along","author":"Christy Frink","date":"2010-08-13T09:30:00-05:00","tags":["bike rental","bike share","free","heat wave","music city star","national parks","power outages","severe weather","shelby park"],"categories":["News"],"contentEncoded":"<div id=\"greet_block\"><noscript><div class=\"greet_block wpgb_cornered\"><div class=\"greet_text\"><div class=\"greet_image\"><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/feed/rss/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://nashvillest.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-greet-box/images/rss_icon.png\" alt=\"WP Greet Box icon\"></a></div>Hello there! If you&apos;re new to Nashvillest, you might want to <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/nashvillest\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>subscribe to our RSS feed</strong></a> to make sure you don&apos;t miss anything! We&apos;re also on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/nashvillest\" target=\"blank\"><strong>Twitter</strong></a> if you&apos;d like to join us there!<div style=\"clear:both\"></div><div class=\"greet_block_powered_by\">Powered by <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/projects/wordpress-plugins/wp-greet-box-wordpress-plugin/\" title=\"WP Greet Box WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WP Greet Box</a> <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/\" title=\"WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WordPress Plugin</a></div><div style=\"clear:both\"></div></div></div></noscript></div><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/roger_m/2624259007/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3188/2624259007_3a1b2fcacc.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"277\" height=\"416\"></a></p><p>Good morning, Nashville. We&#x2019;re in a bit of a hurry this morning, so here is your abbreviated Bright &amp; Early:</p><ul><li>Metro&#x2019;s free bike share program kicked off this morning with a bike ride from Shelby Park to the Music City Star station. The program includes thirty bikes, helmets and locks stored at pick-up locations in Shelby Park and the train station. [<a href=\"http://nashvillecitypaper.com/content/city-news/citys-bike-sharing-program-begin-friday-morning?utm_source=feedburner&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_campaign=Feed:+NashvilleCityPaper-CityNews+(Nashville+City+Paper+-+City+News)&amp;utm_content=Google+Reader\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;nashvillecitypaper.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">City Paper</a>]</li><li>More than 100 National Parks, including several in Tennessee, are free this weekend. Unfortunately you&#x2019;ll still have to brave the one million-degree heat to enjoy them. [<a href=\"http://www.wsmv.com/news/24614978/detail.html\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wsmv.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WSMV</a>]</li><li>However, it is supposed to be slightly cooler this weekend and into next week with a few of those infamous pop-up storms along the way. [<a href=\"http://nashvillewx.com/2010/08/heat-continues-few-pop-up-storms-to-cool-some-down-not-as-hot-next-week/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;nashvillewx.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Nashville WX</a>]</li><li>And who knew pop-up storms could be so disastrous? Between all the downed trees and power lines, West Nashville looked like a war zone last night. [<a href=\"http://www.newschannel5.com/global/story.asp?s=12971543\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.newschannel5.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WTVF</a>]</li><li>The Tennessean takes us on a quick tour of Metro&#x2019;s biggest data breaches in the past few years. [<a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/article/20100813/NEWS0202/8130353/Online+data+breaches+plague+Metro+Nashville\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Tennessean</a>]</li></ul><p><em>Photo by </em><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/roger_m/2624259007/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_self\"><em>Roger M</em></a><em>.</em></p><p>No related posts.</p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<!--END .entry-content .article-->"}